snippet.title: Rebellion Stryker Play-through
snippet.description:
GENRE: 2.5D Shooter

Rebellion Stryker:
In a future where corrupt politicians reign supreme and tyranny grips the cities with an iron fist, a beacon of hope emerges! Enter the Strykers, a fearless band of mercenaries struggling to pay the bills! Tasked by an enigmatic benefactor, Raimu and Rale Guhn embark on a mission to topple the oppressors and restore justice to the people, determined to unravel the mysteries shrouding their elusive client! Get ready for an adrenaline-fueled journey through the shadows of power and intrigue!
